channel.title: Quick flipping for low levels
channel.description:
since i remembered i hate runescape (played for two days and quit), i'm gonna tell you two items that I found really good to flip to turn that 50k into 300k+, this is only helpful if you're starting out from scratch in runescape.
buy dragon boots @ 23k, then sell at 26k buy water talismans @ 5520gp and sell at 5685-5690gp
transactions usually take between 10-30 minutes to complete, and obviously i'm not sure how long this will last now. the profit margin is s[b][/b]hit but it helps bring in a few extra hundred k to get started in making your first mil. obviously the more money you have the more you can buy, and therefore the higher profit. stick with the price guides i stated as these are the ones i found to buy and sell successfully within a reasonable time frame.
